title: UỐNG KHÔNG HẾT ĐỪNG TRÁCH TAU
content:
Tình yêu là những ngày không thể lường trước được người mình yêu định làm cái trò gì.
Ví dụ như đây, thay vì hiên ngang bước vào đặt cốc trà sữa phát bộp lên bàn, mạnh mẽ như một người đàn ông đích thực, rú lên "UỐNG KHÔNG HẾT ĐỪNG TRÁCH TAU!".
Thì người đàn ông của tôi lại chọn rón rén trong chính căn nhà của mình, núp lùm ú oà tôi, nhưng tuổi gì qua được mắt tôi hả hả con lợn này

title: ENHANCEMENT: Notebook - General Clean Up and One Note Field
content: This is a high level description. A confluence document will be created that will provide more information, but this is enough to get started.
body:
• Clean up the presentation of information to reduce wasting space forcing users to scroll. For example, if there are no comments on the annotation, then do not show empty text box where notes would go. If the user selects edit, then it would turn into a text box for a comment to be added. The comments would display as text below the annotation, but as text, not in text box unless being edited.
  • The tags (labels) want to clean up to be typical pill style and when editing, they should get a small x to remove the label. Today it turns to green pill to indicate that it is selected with black text that is hard to read from an accessibility stand point.

title: What capabilities are essential for someone to be considered a full-stack developer?
content: This is a high level description. A confluence document will be created that will provide more information, but this is enough to get started.
body:
A full-stack developer is essentially a jack-of-all-trades in software development, capable of handling front-end, back-end, database management, and server operations single-handedly. This comprehensive skill set is not only a boon for boosting efficiency and cutting costs for businesses but also marks a significant trend in the tech industry. Despite its appealing advantages, the path to becoming a full-stack developer is fraught with challenges, including a steep learning curve and substantial work pressure. Individuals need both solid technical skills and strong mental fortitude to navigate these challenges effectively. The demand for such versatile developers has surged, especially among those looking to make their mark on the global stage.


﻿Becoming a confident full-stack developer and paving your way for global ventures hinges on possessing ten key qualities

title: BUG: "Active" instead of "Needs Grading" status in a Dashboard (updated)
content: This is a high level description. A confluence document will be created that will provide more information, but this is enough to get started.
body:
The demand for specialized rendering solutions grows as applications become more diverse and extend beyond traditional web platforms. The need for custom React renderers arises when developers encounter scenarios where the default rendering approach may not be optimal or when developers are targeting unconventional environments such as mobile applications, virtual reality experiences, or even server-side rendering.


Recognizing this scenario is crucial when developers notice significant performance bottlenecks or limitations in achieving the desired user experience using React’s default rendering. For instance, imagine a financial analytics dashboard within a React application that dynamically visualizes stock market data with numerous live updates and sophisticated charting requirements. In this example, the default rendering approach might not efficiently manage the continuous flow of data and intricate chart computations, signaling the necessity for a tailored rendering solution.
